name: School WIse Total Students
query:
select
    `tabStudent Entry`.school_name as "School Name:Data/School Name",
    `tabStudent Entry`.academic_year as "Academic Year:Link/Academic Year",
    `tabStudent Entry`.district as "District:Link/Districts",
    `tabStudent Entry`.total_student_per_school as "Total Student Per School:Int/Total Student Per School"
from `tabStudent Entry`;
